00:27:43.950 --> 00:27:51.090
And the properties such as
conductivity, diffusivity,

00:27:51.090 --> 00:27:54.310
susceptibility and so on and
all their many varieties,

00:27:54.310 --> 00:27:56.530
these are something
which we'll refer

00:27:56.530 --> 00:27:57.780
to as property tensors.

00:28:03.200 --> 00:28:06.290
And they are tensors
demonstrably, but they are

00:28:06.290 --> 00:28:08.250
tensors which describe
the physical

00:28:08.250 --> 00:28:11.080
behavior of a crystal.

00:28:11.080 --> 00:28:17.905
Nye uses a term that I don't
think is self explanatory, so

00:28:17.905 --> 00:28:18.700
I don't care for it.

00:28:18.700 --> 00:28:20.580
He calls these field tensors.

00:28:26.280 --> 00:28:30.470
That sounds like some
